Achievements.Name: Victory!
Achievements.Description: Finish the game.

Achievements.Name: Music Lover
Achievements.Description: Obtain all song scrolls.

Achievements.Name: Master Angler
Achievements.Description: Successfully fish 5 sparkling fishing spots.

Achievements.Name: Decked Out
Achievements.Description: Purchase or unlock all relics, equipment, and upgrades.

Achievements.Name: Relic Roundtable
Achievements.Description: Defeat an enemy by using each relic.

Achievements.Name: I Scream For Ichor
Achievements.Description: Sample each of the Troupple King's ichors.

Achievements.Name: Nice Hat...
Achievements.Description: Help out all the moochers in the fancy shop.

Achievements.Name: Reflect Lord
Achievements.Description: Hit enemies with a reflected projectile 30 times.

Achievements.Name: Again!
Achievements.Description: Finish New Game Plus.

Achievements.Name: Hall Champion
Achievements.Description: Solve the woes of the Hall of Champions.

Achievements.Name: Well Met
Achievements.Description: Defeat all of the wandering travelers.

Achievements.Name: Halfway
Achievements.Description: Defeat 4 of the Order of No Quarter.

Achievements.Name: Hey Big Spender
Achievements.Description: Spend a combined 25000 gold.

Achievements.Name: No Damage!
Achievements.Description: Finish any Stage without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Impossible!
Achievements.Description: Finish the game without dying.

Achievements.Name: Penny Pincher
Achievements.Description: Finish the game without spending any money.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Platformer
Achievements.Description: Finish the game without falling into a bottomless pit.

Achievements.Name: Checkpointless
Achievements.Description: Destroy every possible checkpoint in the game.

Achievements.Name: First Purchase
Achievements.Description: Buy your first item.

Achievements.Name: Master Shoveler
Achievements.Description: Purchase all available Shovel Blade upgrades.

Achievements.Name: Flare Wander
Achievements.Description: Defeat an enemy with the Flare Wand from more than 25 blocks away.

Achievements.Name: Another Dimension
Achievements.Description: Collect 2000 worth of gold lying on spikes, while using the Phase Locket.

Achievements.Name: Super Sphere
Achievements.Description: Destroy 5 enemies within 5 seconds using Chaos Spheres.

Achievements.Name: Knuckle Down
Achievements.Description: Hang in the air for more than 4 seconds using the Dust Knuckles.

Achievements.Name: Reflected Riches
Achievements.Description: Bounce the same Alchemy Coin 5 times in a row.

Achievements.Name: Arc of Iron
Achievements.Description: Defeat 3 enemies with one Throwing Anchor.

Achievements.Name: Flying Feat
Achievements.Description: Defeat 3 enemies using the Propeller Dagger without touching the ground.

Achievements.Name: Boom!
Achievements.Description: Defeat 5 foes at once using the War Horn.

Achievements.Name: Clearing a Path
Achievements.Description: Run over 5 enemies using the same Mobile Gear.

Achievements.Name: I'm Alive!
Achievements.Description: Finish any stage without dying.

Achievements.Name: True Shovelry
Achievements.Description: Beat the game without collecting any relics.

Achievements.Name: Hurry Up!
Achievements.Description: Finish the game within 1 hour and 30 minutes.

Achievements.Name: Order of Hoarders
Achievements.Description: Have 50000 gold on hand.

Achievements.Name: Get the Point
Achievements.Description: Destroy all checkpoints in a single stage.

Achievements.Name: Untouched
Achievements.Description: Emerge unscathed from a battle with any Knight of the Order of No Quarter.

Achievements.Name: Shovel Economy
Achievements.Description: Finish a level and swing the Shovel Blade fewer than 20 times.

Achievements.Name: On a Diet
Achievements.Description: Finish a level without eating any food.

Achievements.Name: Sparker
Achievements.Description: Finish off any boss using the Ground Spark technique.

Achievements.Name: You're Fired
Achievements.Description: Finish off the Black Knight with a reflected shot.

Achievements.Name: Pungent
Achievements.Description: Listen to all of Croaker's puns.

Achievements.Name: Juggler
Achievements.Description: Impress Mona with your skills.

Achievements.Name: Dirt Poor
Achievements.Description: Don't collect any gold for an entire Order of No Quarter stage.

Achievements.Name: Hooper
Achievements.Description: Bounce on the Hoop Kid's hoop for 5 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Troupple Acolyte
Achievements.Description: Discover the secrets of the Troupple King.

Achievements.Name: Only You
Achievements.Description: Use caution and common sense around campfires.
